00:03:44.284 --> 00:03:46.584
choice for the British royal family,

00:03:46.844 --> 00:03:49.224
but also royals from all over the world,

00:03:49.424 --> 00:03:51.754
as well as the British aristocracy.

00:03:52.774 --> 00:03:56.464
Now, Simon Mann, by all accounts, wasn’t

00:03:56.504 --> 00:03:59.514
a particularly diligent student, and

00:03:59.754 --> 00:04:02.104
