00:04:05.084 --> 00:04:07.564
where British Army officers are trained.

00:04:08.574 --> 00:04:10.804
Soldiering, it seemed, was a

00:04:10.834 --> 00:04:13.254
profession that he was well-suited

00:04:13.254 --> 00:04:16.124
to, and he eventually joined the

00:04:16.144 --> 00:04:19.674
elite Special Air Service, or SAS.

00:04:20.744 --> 00:04:23.964
Now the SAS is essentially the

00:04:24.174 --> 00:04:26.966
